OL,3,CUlster Farmers' Union takes no
OL,4,Cconfidence vote in DAERA
OL,6,FThe Ulster Farmers' Union (UFU)
OL,7,Fexecutive has taken a no-confidence
OL,8,Fvote in the Department of Agriculture,
OL,9,FEnvironment and Rural Affairs (Daera).
OL,11,FThe organisation described the vote
OL,12,Fwhich took place on Wednesday night as
OL,13,Fhaving been unanimous.
OL,15,FUFU president William Irvine said the
OL,16,Fvote represents "deep dissatisfaction"
OL,17,Ffrom his members about how Daera is
OL,18,Fhandling key issues affecting farmers.
