OL,6,FHe said the vote of no-confidence was
OL,7,Ffirst mooted in early summer following
OL,8,Fthe release of the proposed nutrients
OL,9,Faction programme consultation.
OL,11,FHe also complained of an "unjustified
OL,12,Ffocus" on agriculture in terms of
OL,13,Fclimate change and the blue-green
OL,14,Falgae impacting Lough Neagh.
