OL,3,CUlster Farmers' Union takes no
OL,4,Cconfidence vote in DAERA
OL,6,F"We gave Daera time to see if things
OL,7,Fwould improve, but after mounting
OL,8,Ffrustration over the last few months
OL,9,Fon a host of other issues, this vote
OL,10,Fof no-confidence was unanimously
OL,11,Fagreed last night at our executive
OL,12,Fmeeting," he said.
OL,14,F"The result of no-confidence in Daera
OL,15,Frepresents a deep dissatisfaction from
OL,16,FUFU members on how the department is
OL,17,Fhandling key issues affecting farmers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]vD@AOU
