OL,6,FHe added: "There is also the ongoing
OL,7,Funjustified focus on agriculture
OL,8,Fregarding climate change and Lough
OL,9,FNeagh. Plus the recent AFBI data
OL,10,Fbreach and heightened concerns around
OL,11,Fdata security.
OL,13,F"We are prepared to play our part in
OL,14,Fcreating an environmentally and
OL,15,Feconomically sustainable agriculture
OL,16,Findustry, but Daera needs to work with
OL,17,Ffarmers to deliver what is needed, and
OL,18,Fregrettably this has not happened.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOU
