OL,3,CUlster Farmers' Union takes no
OL,4,Cconfidence vote in DAERA
OL,6,F"Our members now have zero confidence
OL,7,Fin Daera's willingness or ability and
OL,8,Fthis unanimous vote of no-confidence
OL,9,Fis unfortunately a very stark
OL,10,Freflection of Daera's failings and
OL,11,Finadequacies."
OL,13,FResponding, a Daera spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"The Department is disappointed to
OL,15,Flearn of the UFU vote. Our door is
OL,16,Falways open to discuss issues with
OL,17,Fthem."
